articles.title: Iran executes 2 men accused of killing security agent during protests - CBC News
articles.description: Iran hanged two men on Saturday for allegedly killing a member of the security forces during nationwide protests that followed the death of 22-year-old Kurdish Iranian woman Mahsa Amini on Sept. 16, drawing condemnation from the European Union, the United Sta…
